.com/news/music/kesha-has-a-10-year-plan-to-dismantle-the-music-industry-piece-by-piece-3799557">she was devising a 10-year plan to “dismantle” the music industry</a> , after <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-and-dr-luke-settle-defamation-lawsuit-3459651">settling her long-running legal battle with Dr. Luke</a> .</p><p> 2025年，Kesha将参加许多英国现场表演。 These include <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-and-ciara-to-play-uk-festival-exclusive-shows-at-mighty-hoopla-2025-3805266">a slot at Mighty Hoopla</a> in London, where she&#39;ll perform alongside <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ciara">Ciara</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kate-nash">Kate Nash</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pixie-lott">Pixie Lott</a> , Loreen, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/vengaboys">Vengaboys</a> , Mutya, Jamelia, Jojo, Erika Jayne, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/g-flip">G Flip</a> and Daniel Bedingfield.</p><p>她还在5月在曼彻斯特和格拉斯哥举行了两次标题演出。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fkesha-tickets%2Fartist%2F1413109" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find any remaining tickets here</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kesha-announces-new-single-yippee-ki-yay-with-t-pain-3848912">Kesha announces new single &#39;Yippee-Ki-Yay&#39; with T-Pain</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
